            <div class="resume-item">
              <h4>A more local experience</h4>
              <p>Eager to move to a smaller (and less expensive) town, I started working as PHP backend web developer in a communication agency in Fribourg, CH. I upgraded and maintained their own content management system, developed custom modules and forms, populated e-shops and catalogs with data from Google Spreadsheets, dealt with mulitisite and multilingual issues, managed Linux servers, HTTPS gateways, SQL databases, migration of websites to new servers, etc. This job still goes on as of Apr 2023.</p>
