              <p>In Aug 2021 I bought a small offgrid property in the Zala region in western Hungary, and lived in that region for 1 year, learning gardening, trying to renovate it etc. while still keeping my remote job as a web dev. I also helped on other friends' terrains. I sold that property in Nov 2022 because of the heavy inflation on heating and on renovation materials, and the lack of motivation to continue, and moved back to Budapest.</p>
